Resist Disease, Resist Cold, Shield of the Arch Magi,<BR>
and DMF.<BR>
<BR>
Now, lets talk about a fight between me a 56 necro<BR>
and a 59 wizzie.  Heres how the fight ensues.<BR>
He got the jump on me tried to root me.  I resist and<BR>
my pet chases him.  He runs for about 10 steps and roots<BR>
my pet.  I chase after him and hit him with splurt<BR>
(1200ish pvp dmg over about 90 sec) he nullfies it<BR>
as his next spell.  While I am casting Ignite blood<BR>
(900 pvp dmg over 120 sec).  I am then hit by an<BR>
unresistable nuke (lure of lightning) which get<BR>
eaten by my Manaskin(600ish hp rune type spell). I<BR>
then deflux him once (210hp 3sec cast lifetap).<BR>
Wait It didnt seem to do anything.  Ohh yeah wizzies<BR>
at level 59 have a serious rune type spell that blows<BR>
manaskin out of the water..  So he then nullifies<BR>
ignite blood.  So far he is down about 20hp and I<BR>
am down 0 hp.  His next spell is another lure spell<BR>
(another unresistable nuke)  That takes my hp down to<BR>
about 2/3rd.  I then try to cast ebolt he resists.<BR>
He casts another lure. I am now down to about 1<BR>
bubble of hp..  Now i run like a screaming little<BR>
girl.  I am sorry but if you cant get the damn dots<BR>
to stick on anything you will die.  At uber levels<BR>
resists are so high that none of these dots will stick<BR>
atleast on a pvp server..  My only hope is that I<BR>
can stick splurt or ignite at the bottom of their<BR>
buff list so they have to turn off all their buffs<BR>
to nullify them...  Otherwise I am pretty much dead.<BR>
Also if you are going into a dual with a necro you<BR>
better keep your top 2 or 3 buff slots open for an<BR>
annul...  <BR>
<BR>
Taleria Reznor<BR>
56 Defiler Tallon Zek.<BR>
