All this stuff took place in less than about 40 sec.<BR>
I was XPing while i got attacked so I didnt have<BR>
harmshield and Shadowstep up.  Even so I wouldnt cast<BR>
shadowstep it gets you xped by landing you near mobs<BR>
in situations like that.
